{
  "stem": "25773.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--tuberculosis.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, I tell it briefly although it is a-- it is a very painful and forever ever memorable time of my life.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Anyway, I used to go out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "At this time was still possible to go out of the--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, but you were not allowed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You were actually not-- but I don't know why-- they were quite friendly, the Germans allowed you to go through the gate.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But if outside the gate, there were Polish boys very often or people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And if they found you, they'd say, Jew, Jew, Jew, Jew, and they took you to the Polish-- you know--",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--to the, to the police.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And especially you were noticeable because you were not allowed in the winter to wear any fur or anything, you know.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But that was-- at this time was already closed, the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- but nonetheless, I used to take this-- we didn't have a yellow badge.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had white and blue I think it was.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we had already the Jewish policemen who were guarding and had to help you know with the keeping order in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mentioned-- I didn't mention before, they were already formed, this police, Jewish police.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they had to keep order with, with, with everlasting, increasing population in the ghetto, which swell afterwards to I think it was 3-- 300-- 300-- 500-- 5,000-- over 300,000 Jews.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Some people say 400,000, some say 300,000.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Anyway, 300,000 perished.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I used to go to, to Otwock and see my brother.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then on one special occasion-- because I don't want to make it long, he already was very, very ill.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he seemed like he was waiting for me to come to die in presence of his family.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, he must have been 20.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
